You were not back home all night.
Am I not worried?

554
00:28:56,599 --> 00:28:58,319
You worked too hard.

555
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:02,040
I've just realized now

556
00:29:02,959 --> 00:29:04,599
how good working is.

557
00:29:05,319 --> 00:29:07,800
Money sometimes is really
more important than love.

558
00:29:08,359 --> 00:29:11,079
If you put efforts into making money,
you'll have it.

559
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:12,359
But love...

560
00:29:12,599 --> 00:29:14,439
Giving doesn't always get paid back.

561
00:29:15,800 --> 00:29:16,880
Pay back?

562
00:29:21,959 --> 00:29:22,599
What?

563
00:29:22,760 --> 00:29:23,520
Du Xiaosu.

564
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:24,560
What am I to you?

565
00:29:24,719 --> 00:29:25,319
My bestie.

566
00:29:25,439 --> 00:29:28,040
I'm your good listener.

567
00:29:28,439 --> 00:29:29,359
So there can't be anything

568
00:29:29,479 --> 00:29:31,599
in your mind, right?

569
00:29:31,760 --> 00:29:33,920
Tell me everything you're upset about.

570
00:29:34,079 --> 00:29:35,400
I am all ears.

571
00:29:37,160 --> 00:29:38,760
What are you talking about?

572
00:29:39,119 --> 00:29:41,000
I'm quite busy now.

573
00:29:41,239 --> 00:29:43,160
I don't have time to
spill out the troubles.

574
00:29:44,319 --> 00:29:45,640
If you don't have anything else,

575
00:29:45,800 --> 00:29:46,880
just go back.

576
00:29:47,119 --> 00:29:48,560
Thank you for dropping in.

577
00:29:48,839 --> 00:29:49,239
Let's go.

578
00:29:49,359 --> 00:29:50,640
Look at your black eyes.

579
00:29:51,359 --> 00:29:52,479
I am busy.

580
00:29:52,959 --> 00:29:54,280
Is this for work?

581
00:29:55,760 --> 00:29:57,000
Isn't it for him?

582
00:29:58,280 --> 00:29:59,656
(Entertainment Express. Lei Yuzheng)

583
00:30:00,280 --> 00:30:01,319
It's been revised.

584
00:30:01,520 --> 00:30:03,239
Fine. Even if it is.

585
00:30:03,680 --> 00:30:04,920
How about Yutian's PR?

586
00:30:05,119 --> 00:30:05,959
How about Xu You's agent?

587
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:07,719
Why don't they come out to
make the clarification?

588
00:30:08,040 --> 00:30:10,319
Now people all over the world are
responding the same.

589
00:30:10,599 --> 00:30:12,079
They are all acquiescing in it.

590
00:30:13,280 --> 00:30:14,719
A clean hand wants no washing.

591
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:15,719
If every time there is a gossip,

592
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:17,400
it has to be clarified,

593
00:30:17,599 --> 00:30:20,000
these companies can't do anything else.

594
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:21,479
Go ahead. You continue to be stubborn.

595
00:30:21,680 --> 00:30:23,079
I'm asking you one question now.

596
00:30:23,319 --> 00:30:25,079
Did he, Lei Yuzheng, ever contact you?

597
00:30:25,239 --> 00:30:25,880
Did he make a call?

598
00:30:26,040 --> 00:30:27,599
Did he send a message?

599
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:30,760
If it's difficult for you to ask,
I will ask him.

600
00:30:32,239 --> 00:30:33,239
What are you doing?

601
00:30:34,599 --> 00:30:35,680
Can't I ask him?

602
00:30:35,800 --> 00:30:37,079
What are you doing?

603
00:30:37,280 --> 00:30:38,359
I have to make it clear.

604
00:30:38,520 --> 00:30:40,760
What? How?

605
00:30:40,959 --> 00:30:42,560
Who am I to Lei Yuzheng?

606
00:30:42,760 --> 00:30:43,719
He has the freedom to contact

607
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:45,079
with others without my permission.

608
00:30:45,280 --> 00:30:47,439
Don't you know that?

609
00:30:47,760 --> 00:30:48,719
What happened to you on the island

610
00:30:48,920 --> 00:30:50,560
demonstrated that you fell in love.

611
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:53,359
I don't understand.

612
00:30:53,520 --> 00:30:55,359
Why can't you intervene?

613
00:30:56,280 --> 00:30:57,640
Besides,

614
00:30:58,079 --> 00:31:00,719
it's not interfering,
it's protecting your right.

615
00:31:03,479 --> 00:31:04,760
Are you really silly?

616
00:31:05,079 --> 00:31:07,199
She's threatening you now.
Are you aware of that?

617
00:31:07,359 --> 00:31:08,680
You're just sitting here
and doing nothing.

618
00:31:08,800 --> 00:31:10,119
Zou Siqi.

619
00:31:12,599 --> 00:31:14,520
Lei Yuzheng and I are grown-ups.

620
00:31:14,800 --> 00:31:15,719
We'll

621
00:31:15,839 --> 00:31:17,400
work it out.

622
00:31:17,719 --> 00:31:19,239
We've been through so much.

623
00:31:19,439 --> 00:31:20,920
And we know each other.

624
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:24,079
If there is understanding between us,

625
00:31:25,599 --> 00:31:27,000
why do we have to say it?

626
00:31:28,359 --> 00:31:29,439
Fine.

627
00:31:30,040 --> 00:31:31,160
I admit.

628
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:34,079
Lei Yuzheng is probably really
in love with you.

629
00:31:35,199 --> 00:31:38,439
Is he able to cope with the passion
of Xu You?

630
00:31:39,119 --> 00:31:41,560
I don't want to speculate on others.

631
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:45,079
When you found that
Lei Yuzheng and Xu You were together,

632
00:31:45,439 --> 00:31:46,719
your expression had already

633
00:31:46,880 --> 00:31:48,160
told me everything.

634
00:31:48,359 --> 00:31:48,800
My lady.

635
00:31:48,920 --> 00:31:51,359
I really don't want to
talk about it today.

636
00:31:51,760 --> 00:31:53,560
I still have a lot of work to do.

637
00:31:53,680 --> 00:31:54,760
I'm really busy.

638
00:31:54,920 --> 00:31:55,719
I'm also tired.

639
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:57,160
If there isn't anything else,

640
00:31:57,239 --> 00:31:59,719
you can go home first.

641
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:02,119
-Hurry up. Du Xiaosu.
-Bye.

642
00:32:02,319 --> 00:32:03,920
I can wish you happy every day.

643
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:06,400
But the premise is

644
00:32:08,599 --> 00:32:10,359
