646
00:32:32,479 --> 00:32:33,119
Mr. Lin.

647
00:32:33,280 --> 00:32:34,439
Something was wrong!

648
00:32:34,560 --> 00:32:35,920
Please come back!

649
00:32:43,079 --> 00:32:44,959
Nurse! Nurse!

650
00:32:45,319 --> 00:32:46,079
Honey. Everything's fine.

651
00:32:46,239 --> 00:32:46,839
Hold on!

652
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:48,079
Nurse!

653
00:32:49,199 --> 00:32:50,040
Everything is gonna be fine.

654
00:32:50,199 --> 00:32:51,239
