655
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:56,680
Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!

656
00:32:56,800 --> 00:32:57,839
Watch out! Watch out!

657
00:32:58,839 --> 00:33:00,400
Come on. Slow down.

658
00:33:00,959 --> 00:33:02,119
The patient's family members
are waiting outside.

659
00:33:20,839 --> 00:33:21,640
Dad.

660
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:22,920
Dad.

661
00:33:23,800 --> 00:33:24,920
Fanlv is in trouble.

662
00:33:39,479 --> 00:33:40,760
Settle her down quickly.

663
00:33:50,040 --> 00:33:51,399
