664
00:33:52,199 --> 00:33:53,639
Just let me die.

665
00:33:54,600 --> 00:33:56,639
We've worked so hard to
save you.

666
00:33:56,840 --> 00:33:57,919
You still wanna die?

667
00:33:58,159 --> 00:33:58,959
Do you know

668
00:33:59,120 --> 00:34:00,600
how many patients in the world die

669
00:34:00,760 --> 00:34:02,479
without treatment every day?

670
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:04,959
Look at those patients
who are seriously ill.

671
00:34:05,360 --> 00:34:06,600
They are so painful,

672
00:34:07,080 --> 00:34:08,439
but they are still pulling
themselves together.

673
00:34:08,760 --> 00:34:09,840
You're so young,

674
00:34:10,080 --> 00:34:12,120
but you don't cherish your life,

675
00:34:12,439 --> 00:34:14,159
and the efforts of medical staff.

676
00:34:14,439 --> 00:34:15,080
So many opportunities for patients

677
00:34:15,239 --> 00:34:16,639
waiting for rescue are wasted.

678
00:34:20,439 --> 00:34:21,840
The wound has been treated.

679
00:34:22,479 --> 00:34:23,919
Think about it.

680
00:34:30,120 --> 00:34:31,239
Who are you?

681
00:34:31,879 --> 00:34:32,959
I'm the patient's husband.

682
00:34:33,399 --> 00:34:34,239
Doctor.

683
00:34:34,760 --> 00:34:36,159
How is my wife now?

684
00:34:36,479 --> 00:34:37,639
She's fine for now.

685
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:39,199
But,

686
00:34:39,439 --> 00:34:41,199
is there something wrong with your wife?

687
00:34:41,399 --> 00:34:43,879
Or something made her unhappy?

688
00:34:44,639 --> 00:34:45,560
She had depression before.

689
00:34:45,719 --> 00:34:47,239
But I didn't expect
it to be so serious.

690
00:34:48,120 --> 00:34:49,479
This time she's lucky.

691
00:34:49,639 --> 00:34:51,120
But it doesn't mean that
she can still be lucky next time.

692
00:34:51,520 --> 00:34:53,040
You have to be prepared.

693
00:34:55,439 --> 00:34:56,520
Please go ahead.

694
00:34:56,719 --> 00:34:57,600
Your wife

695
00:34:58,159 --> 00:34:59,959
has developed
a serious suicidal tendency.

696
00:35:00,159 --> 00:35:01,399
It belongs to severe depression.

697
00:35:01,679 --> 00:35:02,959
I recommend early treatment.

698
00:35:03,199 --> 00:35:05,080
Doctor, I will cooperate with
any treatment required.

699
00:35:05,280 --> 00:35:05,800
Money is not the problem,

700
00:35:05,959 --> 00:35:07,080
as long as she can be cured.

701
00:35:07,320 --> 00:35:09,120
First of all, drug therapy can be
taken into consideration.

702
00:35:10,280 --> 00:35:11,360
Drug therapy?

703
00:35:11,520 --> 00:35:13,399
Of course, the patient like her

704
00:35:13,760 --> 00:35:14,760
needs long-term medication.

705
00:35:14,919 --> 00:35:16,959
She might be drug dependent.

706
00:35:17,120 --> 00:35:18,719
There'll be trigeminal neuralgia,

707
00:35:18,919 --> 00:35:19,600
memory loss,

708
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:21,199
and damages to visceral organs, etc.

709
00:35:22,199 --> 00:35:23,719
Is there any other way?

710
00:35:24,239 --> 00:35:25,360
If you don't adopt drug therapy,

711
00:35:25,639 --> 00:35:27,159
then try psychological treatment.

712
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:30,000
The best psychotherapy is
to keep her company.

713
00:35:30,199 --> 00:35:31,520
Your family members have to
accompany her as much as possible.

714
00:35:31,879 --> 00:35:33,199
Help her relieve the pressure,

715
00:35:33,439 --> 00:35:34,439
and ensure her safety.

716
00:35:34,639 --> 00:35:37,000
Besides, the patient is quite agitated.

717
00:35:37,159 --> 00:35:38,959
It's better not to let her know
about her illness,

718
00:35:39,120 --> 00:35:40,600
so as not to bother her.

719
00:35:41,600 --> 00:35:42,959
Ok. Thank you, doctor.

720
00:35:43,159 --> 00:35:44,239
All right. You're welcome.

721
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:03,919
Fanlv.

722
00:36:04,879 --> 00:36:06,399
If anything really happens to you,

723
00:36:07,280 --> 00:36:09,040
how can I live the rest of my life?

724
00:36:10,439 --> 00:36:14,120
If I'm dead, everyone will be easy.

725
00:36:14,520 --> 00:36:15,760
Isn't it?

726
00:36:17,040 --> 00:36:18,479
Why are you saying like that?

727
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:20,199
Fanlv.

728
00:36:21,520 --> 00:36:23,399
Do I behave disgracefully in your heart?

729
00:36:23,639 --> 00:36:25,760
People say
couple for one day, love forever.

730
00:36:26,040 --> 00:36:27,959
Moreover,
we've been married for so long.

731
00:36:36,479 --> 00:36:38,239
The doctor told me to be nice to you.

732
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:43,280
Don't lie to me.

733
00:36:45,199 --> 00:36:47,159
I know what's wrong with me.

734
00:36:48,840 --> 00:36:50,439
Why did you save me?

735
00:36:52,040 --> 00:36:53,719
It'll be good that I'm dead.

736
00:36:55,399 --> 00:36:57,280
What's the point of living?

737
00:36:58,040 --> 00:36:59,879
It'll be easy instead to be dead.

738
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:03,000
Fanlv.

739
00:37:03,560 --> 00:37:04,719
Don't say that.

740
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:07,000
Each person will be
in a bad mood sometimes .

741
00:37:08,439 --> 00:37:09,520
The doctor said

742
00:37:10,280 --> 00:37:11,919
you would get better very soon.

743
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:17,199
Dad.

744
00:37:17,360 --> 00:37:18,320
Get up.

745
00:37:25,679 --> 00:37:29,520
My dear. What's wrong with you?

746
00:37:30,919 --> 00:37:33,159
Are you silly?

747
00:37:33,719 --> 00:37:35,679
If anything happens to you,

748
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:38,520
how can I

749
00:37:39,520 --> 00:37:41,479
live with it?

750
00:37:45,800 --> 00:37:46,919
Dad.

751
00:37:49,080 --> 00:37:52,399
My dear. Why are you so upset?

752
00:37:54,679 --> 00:37:56,600
Tell me if you are in trouble.

753
00:37:57,280 --> 00:37:58,840
Dad will help you out.

754
00:38:07,320 --> 00:38:08,280
Come with me.

755
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:23,639
Tell me. What's going on?

756
00:38:24,360 --> 00:38:28,000
Dad. I didn't take good care of Fanlv.

757
00:38:28,199 --> 00:38:29,679
Sure, you didn't.

758
00:38:30,600 --> 00:38:31,560
Let me ask you.

759
00:38:32,439 --> 00:38:33,600
What did the doctor say?

760
00:38:33,879 --> 00:38:34,919
The doctor said

761
00:38:35,919 --> 00:38:37,280
Fanlv had depression.

762
00:38:37,520 --> 00:38:38,879
When did she have it?

763
00:38:39,719 --> 00:38:41,639
Why don't you tell me earlier?

764
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:45,199
Actually Fanlv has been
in depression for a while.

765
00:38:45,439 --> 00:38:48,080
I didn't tell you because I'm
afraid you might be worried.

766
00:38:49,959 --> 00:38:52,040
Fanlv is my daughter.

767
00:38:52,439 --> 00:38:54,520
When she was sick, you didn't tell me.

768
00:38:54,840 --> 00:38:56,719
You were worrying about me?

769
00:38:57,040 --> 00:38:58,719
If you really worried about me,

770
00:38:59,000 --> 00:39:01,879
you would not fight with her recklessly.

771
00:39:02,120 --> 00:39:04,320
You made her lose her baby.

772
00:39:05,879 --> 00:39:08,280
Lin Xiangyuan.
I'm telling you.

773
00:39:10,080 --> 00:39:12,080
You should consider yourself lucky
that nothing happened to Fanlv.

774
00:39:12,320 --> 00:39:13,800
If anything happens to her,

775
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:15,439
I won't forgive you.

776
00:39:16,439 --> 00:39:19,280
Dad. It's my fault.

777
00:39:19,560 --> 00:39:21,320
I didn't make Fanlv happy.

778
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:24,280
So far,

779
00:39:24,600 --> 00:39:26,760
I assume that it's time to end.

